Generic single-database configuration for Alembic migrations.

## Running Migrations

### In Development (Local)
```bash
cd gps-tracker/backend
alembic upgrade head
```

### In Production (Docker)
```bash
cd ~/gps-tracker
docker-compose exec backend bash -c "cd /app && alembic upgrade head"
```

### Check Current Version
```bash
# Local
alembic current

# Docker
docker-compose exec backend bash -c "cd /app && alembic current"
```

### Create New Migration
```bash
# Local
alembic revision -m "description of changes"

# Autogenerate from models
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"
```

## Migration Files
- `env.py` - Alembic environment configuration
- `script.py.mako` - Template for new migrations
- `versions/` - Directory containing all migration scripts
